@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_buenwz(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = tmp
    tmp = (wp.cos(v0) - tmp)
    v1 = wp.exp(0.70)
    v2 = (wp.cos((v0 + 0.95 * tmp + 0.90)) * wp.sin(wp.sin(v1 + 0.75)))
    v1 = v0
    v2 = wp.abs(((v1 + 0.84 * v1 + 0.21) + v2))
    tmp = (tmp * wp.cos((v0 + 0.84 + v1 + 0.17)))
    data[tid] = v0
